《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》市场反应非常好，在日本首周（4天）即售出936,734套，成为日本首周销量最高的Wii游戏。<ref>{{cite web | author=Alexander, Leigh | date=2009-12-07 | title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii Sees Biggest Wii Debut Ever In Japan | url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26393/New_Super_Mario_Bros_Wii_Sees_Biggest_Wii_Debut_Ever_In_Japan.php | publisher=Gamasutra | accessdate=2009-12-07 | archive-date=2009-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091210201012/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26393/New_Super_Mario_Bros_Wii_Sees_Biggest_Wii_Debut_Ever_In_Japan.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>次周销量继续涨至1,401,558套。<ref>{{cite web|author=Gantayat, Anoop |date=2009-12-16 |title=Major Sales Feats for Wii and PS3 |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2009/12/16/wii_and_ps3_sales_feats/ |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=2009-12-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120721222519/http://andriasang.com/comez1/wii_and_ps3_sales_feats/ |archivedate=2012-07-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》也以7周3,002,753套的成绩，成为日本最快卖出300万套的游戏。<ref>{{cite web | author=Alexander, Leigh | date=2010-01-19 | title=NSMB Wii Fastest Title Ever To Top 3 Million In Japan | url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26869/NSMB_Wii_Fastest_Title_Ever_To_Top_3_Million_In_Japan.php | publisher=Gamasutra | accessdate=2010-01-19 | archive-date=2010-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122013741/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/26869/NSMB_Wii_Fastest_Title_Ever_To_Top_3_Million_In_Japan.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>而在发售一年后，《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》成为继FC平台的《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》和PS平台上《勇者斗恶龙VII 伊甸的战士们》之后历史上第三款在日本本土销量超过400万套的家用游戏主机平台游戏。<ref name="MobyGames">{{cite web |url=http://www.mobygames.com/game/wii/new-super-mario-bros-wii/trivia |title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii for Wii (2009) Trivia |publisher=MobyGames |date=2009-12-27 |accessdate=2011-06-08 |archive-date=2012-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410222653/http://www.mobygames.com/game/wii/new-super-mario-bros-wii/trivia |dead-url=no }}</ref>在北美本作同样叫座，2009年11月总计售出1,390,000套，以仅次于[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]版《[[使命召唤：现代战争2|使命召唤：现代战争2]]》的当月销量位居第三。<ref>{{cite web | author=Kohler, Chris | date=2009-12-10 | title=November NPD: Modern Warfare Shifts 6 Million Copies | url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/12/november-2009-npd/ | publisher=Wired | accessdate=2009-12-10 | archive-date=2009-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091212154109/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/12/november-2009-npd/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》在美国已售出4,000,000套<ref>{{cite web| author= Pavel Alpeyev| date= 2010-01-05| title= Nintendo Shares Rise After Record Wii Sales in U.S.| publisher= [[BusinessWeek|BusinessWeek]]| url= http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-01-05/nintendo-shares-rise-after-record-wii-sales-in-u-s-update2-.html| accessdate= 2010-01-05| archive-date= 2010-01-10| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100110004944/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-01-05/nintendo-shares-rise-after-record-wii-sales-in-u-s-update2-.html| dead-url= no}}</ref>，全球销量超过10,000,000套，以此成为史上销售速度最快的单平台游戏。<ref>{{cite web | date=2010-01-24 | title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii Passes 10 Million Units Sold | url=http://www.gamingunion.net/news/new-super-mario-bros-wii-passes-10-million-units-sold--917.html | publisher=GamingUnion.net | accessdate=2010-01-24 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100127070545/http://www.gamingunion.net/news/new-super-mario-bros-wii-passes-10-million-units-sold--917.html | archivedate=2010年1月27日 }}</ref>虽然其首月销量并未超越《现代战争2》，分析家Jesse Divnich相信这一局面终将实现，他表示：“毫无疑问，《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》从长期看必将凌驾于其竞争者之上。”<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3177277|title=NPD Fallout: Mario vs Modern Warfare|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP]]|accessdate=2009-12-30}}</ref>这一分析可谓不无根据，因为任天堂北美总裁[[雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米|雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米]]也曾豪言《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》的美国销量将在三个月内赶超《现代战争2》。<ref name="#1"/>

截至2015年3月，游戏共售出2932万套。这使其成为销量第四的Wii平台游戏，同时也是Wii上销量第二的马里奥游戏，仅次于《[[马里奥赛车Wii|马里奥赛车Wii]]》。<ref name="mar15">{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/sales/software/wii.html|title=Top Selling Software Sales Units - Wii Software|publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date=2015-03-31|accessdate=2015-05-12|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009225646/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/en/sales/software/wii.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 媒体评价 ===
游戏获得了业内媒体的肯定。日本游戏杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》称赞本作是“2D动作游戏杰作”，并评予游戏40/40的满分，使其成为23年来第13部、也是Wii平台第4部满分游戏。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3177082|title=Japan Review Check: New SMB, Assassin's, Left 4 Dead 2|last=Gifford|first=Kevin|date=2009-11-25|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5411569/famitsu-awards-new-super-mario-bros-wii-a-perfect-score|title=Famitsu Awards New Super Mario Bros. Wii A Perfect Score|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|date=2009-11-24|publisher=Kotaku|accessdate=2009-12-10|archive-date=2009-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091212203208/http://kotaku.com/5411569/famitsu-awards-new-super-mario-bros-wii-a-perfect-score|dead-url=no}}</ref> 英国《[[Official_Nintendo_Magazine|Official Nintendo Magazine]]》给予本作96%分，并特别称赞了游戏对细节的注重和多人模式。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/article.php?id=13312|title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii|last=Scullion|first=Chris|date=2009-11-18|work=Official Nintendo Magazine|accessdate=2009-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091121135714/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/article.php?id=13312|archive-date=2009-11-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>《[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]》评予9.0分，认为游戏的单人模式更为出色。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=226725|title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii Review|last=Jackson|first=Mike|date=2009-11-05|work=Computer and Video Games|accessdate=2009-12-10|archive-date=2010-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102163235/http://computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=226725|dead-url=no}}</ref>游戏业界网IGN澳洲为《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》打出9.2分，称其多人合作模式是一大“突破”，并赞扬其很好地还原了令超级马里奥兄弟系列风靡全球的游戏方式。<ref>{{cite web|last=Kolan|first=Patrick|title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii AU Review|publisher=IGN AU|date=2009-11-09|accessdate=2009-11-10|url=http://wii.ign.com/articles/104/1043698p1.html|archive-date=2009-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091111161231/http://wii.ign.com/articles/104/1043698p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> IGN美国评予游戏8.9分，称其核心游戏性十分卓越，但也指出游戏缺乏在线模式。不过，[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]却并不以此为缺点，认为在线游戏多以竞争为主，而《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》则是需要从合作中获得快乐的。<ref>{{cite web|last=Scott|first=Ryan|title=The Consensus: New Super Mario Bros. Wii Review|publisher=Gamespy|date=2009-11-13|accessdate=2009-11-14|url=http://wii.gamespy.com/wii/super-mario-wii-2/1045348p1.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091117083344/http://wii.gamespy.com/wii/super-mario-wii-2/1045348p1.html|archive-date=2009-11-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]评予A+级，指出游戏不仅吸收了前作的创新元素，还能让各类玩家都有所收获。<ref>{{cite web|last=Parish|first=Jeremy|title=New Super Mario Bros (Wii) Review|publisher=1UP|date=2009-11-13|accessdate=2009-11-13|url=http://www.1up.com/do/reviewPage?cId=3176906}}</ref>游戏博客[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]高度评价了本游戏，并将其列为购买Wii的原因之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5403839/new-super-mario-bros-wii-review-go-buy-a-wii|title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii Review: Go Buy A Wii|last=Crecente|first=Brian|date=2009-11-13|publisher=Kotaku|accessdate=2009-12-10|archive-date=2009-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091212200532/http://kotaku.com/5403839/new-super-mario-bros-wii-review-go-buy-a-wii|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{tsl|en|X-Play|}}》的Morgan Webb评予4/5分，并赞赏了游戏的关卡难度。<ref name="xplay"/>

不过，英国杂志《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》只给出7/10分，称其缺乏马里奥的传统魅力，画质槽糕而且过于简单。<ref name="EdgeReview">《Edge》，2009年12月刊，86页</ref>[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]同样打出7/10分，认为本作与系列其他作品相比缺乏创新。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/wii/new-super-mario-bros-wii/review/new-super-mario-bros-wii/a-20091113105237874009/g-2009060211259405068/p-3|title=New Super Mario Bros Wii|last=Elston|first=Brett|date=2009-11-13|publisher=GamesRadar|pages=3|accessdate=2009-12-10|archive-date=2011-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615233127/http://www.gamesradar.com/wii/new-super-mario-bros-wii/review/new-super-mario-bros-wii/a-20091113105237874009/g-2009060211259405068/p-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]》更是打出C+的低分，称其为“迄今最不值得一提的马里奥游戏”， 并认为本作乏善可陈，显露出马里奥游戏骨子里的千篇一律。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://origin.avclub.com/articles/new-super-mario-bros-wii,35648/|title=New Super Mario Bros. Wii|last=Teti|first=John|date=2009-11-23|work=The A.V. Club|accessdate=2009-12-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091229220901/http://origin.avclub.com/articles/new-super-mario-bros-wii,35648/|archivedate=2009年12月29日}}</ref>《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》则反驳说，本游戏作为一款续作，自然需要在保留马里奥游戏原先特色的同时加入新亮点。<ref name="v249" />

=== 获奖 ===
《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》在2009年斯派克电子游戏盛典（{{lang|en|Spike Video Game Awards}}）上获得了“最佳Wii游戏”奖项。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nintendoeverything.com/29407/list-of-spike-tv-video-game-awards-2009-winners/|title=List of Spike TV Video Game Awards 2009 winners|date=2009-12-12|work=nintendoeverything.com|accessdate=2013-04-04}}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref> [[IGN|IGN]]也将本作评为“2009年Wii年度游戏”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bestof.ign.com/2009/wii/wii-game-of-the-year.html |title=Wii Wii Game of the Year 2009 - New Super Mario Bros |publisher=Bestof.ign.com |date= |accessdate=2011-06-08 |archive-date=2011-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111021130652/http://bestof.ign.com/2009/wii/wii-game-of-the-year.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 游戏网站[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]将本作选为“2009年最佳Wii游戏”。<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted: Dec 30, 2009 |url=http://www.gametrailers.com/video/best-wii-gt-goty/60269 |title=GameTrailers Game Of The Year Awards 2009 Video Game, Best Wii Game | Video Clip | Game Trailers & Videos |publisher=GameTrailers.com |date=2009-12-30 |accessdate=2011-06-08 |archive-date=2011-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110119082750/http://www.gametrailers.com/video/best-wii-gt-goty/60269 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 游戏还获得了雅虎2009年游戏大奖中的“年度最佳家庭游戏”奖项，<ref name="MobyGames"/>，以及任天堂力量奖的2009年度最佳Wii游戏<ref>{{cite journal|editor=Thomason, Steve|journal=Nintendo Power|issue=252|date=March 2010|title=The 2009 Nintendo Power Awards|pages=56}}</ref>。2010年9月，由日本电脑娱乐供应商协会（CESA）主办的日本游戏大赏2010上，《新超级马里奥兄弟Wii》获得了最高奖项“大赏”。<ref>{{cite web|date=2010-09-16|url=http://awards.cesa.or.jp/2010/press/pdf/100916_year.pdf|format=PDF|title=日本ゲーム大賞2010「年間作品部門」受賞作品決定！|publisher=一般社団法人コンピュータエンターテインメント協会|language=ja|accessdate=2013-04-07|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703053042/http://awards.cesa.or.jp/2010/press/pdf/100916_year.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

